ion",{"title":385,"_path":386},"SS(SSR)","/gists/vpn",{"title":388,"_path":389},"VS Code 插件开发","/gists/vscode-plugin",{"title":391,"_path":392},"Web Components","/gists/web-components",{"title":394,"_path":395},"Windows","/gists/windows",{"title":397,"_path":398},"查缺补漏","/gists/wrong",{"title":400,"_path":401,"children":402},"代码笔记 / Gists","/source-code",[403],{"title":404,"_path":401},"🚄 代码笔记",{"title":406,"_path":407,"children":408},"我 / Abount","/hire",[409],{"title":410,"_path":407},"📬 技术简历",{"title":412,"_path":413,"children":414},"todo","/todo",[415],{"title":412,"_path":413},{"_path":417,"_dir":418,"_draft":419,"_partial":420,"_locale":421,"title":422,"description":421,"body":423,"_type":919,"_id":920,"_source":921,"_file":922,"_stem":923,"_extension":924},"/maps/_business/_low-code/budibase","_low-code",false,true,"","Budibase",{"type":424,"children":425,"toc":915},"root",[426,442,448,456,461,466,475,480,485,490,495,500,505,540,554,559,564,571,576,581,588,593,605,612,617,622,627,632,639,644,649,656,661,683,688,695,700,707,712,719,724,731,745,750,755,760,767,772,779,784,795,800,807,812,819,826,831,838,843,850,855,862,867,874,879,886,891,898,903,910],{"type":427,"tag":428,"props":429,"children":431},"element","h2",{"id":430},"twitter",[432],{"type":427,"tag":433,"props":434,"children":438},"a",{"href":435,"rel":436},"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation",[437],"nofollow",[439],{"type":440,"value":441},"text","Twitter",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":444,"children":445},"p",{},[446],{"type":440,"value":447},"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlackHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":449,"children":450},{},[451],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":453,"children":455},"img",{"alt":421,"src":454},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":457,"children":458},{},[459],{"type":440,"value":460},"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即“也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题”，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":462,"children":463},{},[464],{"type":440,"value":465},"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了“定制化软件开发”需求的广阔场景。",{"type":427,"tag":467,"props":468,"children":469},"blockquote",{},[470],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":471,"children":472},{},[473],{"type":440,"value":474},"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":476,"children":477},{},[478],{"type":440,"value":479},"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":481,"children":482},{},[483],{"type":440,"value":484},"“when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together”，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":486,"children":487},{},[488],{"type":440,"value":489},"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":491,"children":492},{},[493],{"type":440,"value":494},"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":496,"children":497},{},[498],{"type":440,"value":499},"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":501,"children":502},{},[503],{"type":440,"value":504},"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的：",{"type":427,"tag":506,"props":507,"children":508},"ul",{},[509,520,530],{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":511,"children":512},"li",{},[513],{"type":427,"tag":433,"props":514,"children":517},{"href":515,"rel":516},"https://x.com/PoryHQ",[437],[518],{"type":440,"value":519},"PoryHQ",{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":521,"children":522},{},[523],{"type":427,"tag":433,"props":524,"children":527},{"href":525,"rel":526},"https://x.com/bildrHQ",[437],[528],{"type":440,"value":529},"bildrHQ",{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":531,"children":532},{},[533],{"type":427,"tag":433,"props":534,"children":537},{"href":535,"rel":536},"https://x.com/draftbit",[437],[538],{"type":440,"value":539},"draftbit",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":541,"children":542},{},[543,545,552],{"type":440,"value":544},"有个 Tag 叫做 ",{"type":427,"tag":546,"props":547,"children":549},"code",{"className":548},[],[550],{"type":440,"value":551},"#100DaysOfNoCode",{"type":440,"value":553},"，看着不错。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":555,"children":556},{},[557],{"type":440,"value":558},"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":560,"children":561},{},[562],{"type":440,"value":563},"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）：",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":565,"children":566},{},[567],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":568,"children":570},{"alt":421,"src":569},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":572,"children":573},{},[574],{"type":440,"value":575},"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":577,"children":578},{},[579],{"type":440,"value":580},"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给“测试”。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":582,"children":583},{},[584],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":585,"children":587},{"alt":421,"src":586},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":589,"children":590},{},[591],{"type":440,"value":592},"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据“In the distant past, there was a proverbial “digital divide” that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn’t.”推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的“数字鸿沟”出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，AirTable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了“而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker”等公司，但是我没有用过。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":594,"children":595},{},[596,603],{"type":427,"tag":433,"props":597,"children":600},{"href":598,"rel":599},"https://nocodelist.co/",[437],[601],{"type":440,"value":602},"NocodeList",{"type":440,"value":604},"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":606,"children":607},{},[608],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":609,"children":611},{"alt":421,"src":610},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":613,"children":614},{},[615],{"type":440,"value":616},"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":618,"children":619},{},[620],{"type":440,"value":621},"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":623,"children":624},{},[625],{"type":440,"value":626},"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":628,"children":629},{},[630],{"type":440,"value":631},"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格：",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":633,"children":634},{},[635],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":636,"children":638},{"alt":421,"src":637},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":640,"children":641},{},[642],{"type":440,"value":643},"2020-12-20 称自己是“open organization”，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":645,"children":646},{},[647],{"type":440,"value":648},"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":650,"children":651},{},[652],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":653,"children":655},{"alt":421,"src":654},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":657,"children":658},{},[659],{"type":440,"value":660},"“将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币”这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。",{"type":427,"tag":506,"props":662,"children":663},{},[664,668,673,678],{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":665,"children":666},{},[667],{"type":440,"value":441},{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":669,"children":670},{},[671],{"type":440,"value":672},"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github",{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":674,"children":675},{},[676],{"type":440,"value":677},"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用",{"type":427,"tag":510,"props":679,"children":680},{},[681],{"type":440,"value":682},"更新 Readme",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":684,"children":685},{},[686],{"type":440,"value":687},"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（“Build business apps 50x faster”）：",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":689,"children":690},{},[691],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":692,"children":694},{"alt":421,"src":693},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":696,"children":697},{},[698],{"type":440,"value":699},"“As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide opportunities. Optimizing processes, analyzing data, & equipping staff with the right tools is often an easier win for many companies; this is where low-code platforms will continue to succeed.”，最有意思的配图。包括上文提到的 2025 软件定制需求前瞻一文中的配图，都是相同类型的矢量图，很有意思。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":701,"children":702},{},[703],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":704,"children":706},{"alt":421,"src":705},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032152157.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":708,"children":709},{},[710],{"type":440,"value":711},"2021 年初，关于希望使用哪个平台托管 bb，居然没有 AWS。前两名 Heroku 和 DigitalOcean 几乎占据了 100% 的投票。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":713,"children":714},{},[715],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":716,"children":718},{"alt":421,"src":717},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032154794.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":720,"children":721},{},[722],{"type":440,"value":723},"还有另一个投票也显示了 Twitter 上用户的数据库偏好，第一名居然是 Google Sheets。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":725,"children":726},{},[727],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":728,"children":730},{"alt":421,"src":729},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032156394.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":732,"children":733},{},[734,736,743],{"type":440,"value":735},"推荐了一个如何启动开源项目并扩大其影响力的网站，里面有一系列文章：",{"type":427,"tag":433,"props":737,"children":740},{"href":738,"rel":739},"https://opensource.guide/",[437],[741],{"type":440,"value":742},"Open Source Guides",{"type":440,"value":744},"。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":746,"children":747},{},[748],{"type":440,"value":749},"Tech Nation 的 Rising Stars 3 奖项包含了 bb。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":751,"children":752},{},[753],{"type":440,"value":754},"2021-04-13 招聘 3 名 JavaScript 工程师。基于之前他发过关于 Svelte 的迷因，我猜创始人对 Svelte 依旧比较感兴趣。同月 25 号，bb 赞助了 Svelte Summit。直到次年 1 月，他们才开始招聘产品负责人、JS 工程师、产品教育经历、产品设计和客户成功经理，可见扩张得比较节制。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":756,"children":757},{},[758],{"type":440,"value":759},"那么，下一步是什么？我也想问。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":761,"children":762},{},[763],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":764,"children":766},{"alt":421,"src":765},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032244873.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":768,"children":769},{},[770],{"type":440,"value":771},"百姓网的知识库里面也有很多内部应用，但是年久失修。我管他们叫幽灵应用。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":773,"children":774},{},[775],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":776,"children":778},{"alt":421,"src":777},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032251644.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":780,"children":781},{},[782],{"type":440,"value":783},"2021-10-22 发布了新的响应式拖拽，看起来用户体验很好。PRay 马上跟进。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":785,"children":786},{},[787],{"type":427,"tag":788,"props":789,"children":792},"video",{"src":790,"controls":420,"width":791},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032256999.mp4","100%",[793],{"type":440,"value":794},"Your browser does not support the video tag.",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":796,"children":797},{},[798],{"type":440,"value":799},"不过 bb 的界面很总是看起来很“Notion”。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":801,"children":802},{},[803],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":804,"children":806},{"alt":421,"src":805},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032308303.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":808,"children":809},{},[810],{"type":440,"value":811},"2021-11-16 日，“经过两年的开发，我们激动的宣布正式在 product hunt 上进行官方宣传”。而他们的商业化也确实非常成功。2022-10-03 甚至创办了 5000 刀的低代码马拉松。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":813,"children":814},{},[815],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":816,"children":818},{"alt":421,"src":817},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032310378.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":820,"children":821},{},[822],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":823,"children":825},{"alt":421,"src":824},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032318431.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":827,"children":828},{},[829],{"type":440,"value":830},"这一切可能都归功于低代码的魔法。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":832,"children":833},{},[834],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":835,"children":837},{"alt":421,"src":836},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032320756.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":839,"children":840},{},[841],{"type":440,"value":842},"其中有非常长的一段时间，他们的 Twitter 都是围绕推广和新闻展开，没有其他内容的讨论。直到 2022-11 左右。此时，他们拿到了 @SignalFire 领投的 700 万美元融资。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":844,"children":845},{},[846],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":847,"children":849},{"alt":421,"src":848},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032316070.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":851,"children":852},{},[853],{"type":440,"value":854},"拿到融资后，Belfast 决定扩大团队规模。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":856,"children":857},{},[858],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":859,"children":861},{"alt":421,"src":860},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032326207.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":863,"children":864},{},[865],{"type":440,"value":866},"Joe Johnston 解释了为何要从 nocode 转型 lowcode。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":868,"children":869},{},[870],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":871,"children":873},{"alt":421,"src":872},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032329318.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":875,"children":876},{},[877],{"type":440,"value":878},"2023 年有许多更新，比如键盘操作，ISO 27001 认证等。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":880,"children":881},{},[882],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":883,"children":885},{"alt":421,"src":884},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032336236.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":887,"children":888},{},[889],{"type":440,"value":890},"最近一年更新了许多教程，这段时间他们对外宣称自己是“表单创建工具”，并且在博客上也两次拿其他表单创建工具做对比。期间放出不少有意思的应用展示，比如 GPT 克隆（2024-03-11）：",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":892,"children":893},{},[894],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":895,"children":897},{"alt":421,"src":896},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032340672.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":899,"children":900},{},[901],{"type":440,"value":902},"在商业化上变得更加大胆，比如推出 Paid Only 功能。",{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":904,"children":905},{},[906],{"type":427,"tag":452,"props":907,"children":909},{"alt":421,"src":908},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032343927.png",[],{"type":427,"tag":443,"props":911,"children":912},{},[913],{"type":440,"value":914},"在最近（2024-11）的 3.0 更新中，他们解释了之后的路线，主要会包含 AI 相关功能的改进。",{"title":421,"searchDepth":916,"depth":916,"links":917},2,[918],{"id":430,"depth":916,"text":441},"markdown","content:6.maps:_business:_low-code:budibase.md","content","6.maps/_business/_low-code/budibase.md","6.maps/_business/_low-code/budibase","md",[926,929],{"_path":927,"title":928,"description":421},"/maps/_brain/attention","注意力",{"_path":930,"title":931,"description":932},"/maps/_business/_low-code/dynamo","Dynamo","Dynamo 原本是 Revit 中建筑信息模型 (BIM) 的附加模块，后来发展成熟，成为一个给设计师探索可视化编程、解决问题并自行制作工具的平台。",1738603240452]